title: Would you be comfortable in this home? Res Lease in Round Rock. 4 Beds, 3 Baths
posting_body: ['Welcome to Wonderful!', 'Located in the highly desired Sonoma community, this spacious home boasts soaring ceilings, 2 living areas downstairs, an open kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, formal dining & a breakfast nook!', 'Head upstairs to a large game room / 3rd living area featuring fantastic shelving, a huge primary suite with a separate shower and garden tub, 2 additional bedrooms, and ample closet space!', 'Sonoma is located with an easy drive to the newly opened Kalahari Resort and indoor waterpark - summer fun all year long.', 'Also enjoy close proximity to Dell Diamond, Old Settlers Park and Play for All Abilities Park, and the Brushy Creek Regional Trail and downtown Round Rock for eating and entertainment.', 'Conveniently located near Toll 130, Toll 45, I35, Hwy 79 - get to where you want to go quickly from here.', 'Assigned to the highly-rated RRISD elementary and middle schools.', 'This is a MUST SEE!', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 7019528)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Macklin Cahill, Legacy Oak Realty']
